[Cheng Pengfei]

5
00:02:04,150 --> 00:02:05,950
Did my mom introduce you to come?

6
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:09,750
What's your name?

7
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:10,910
Cheng Pengfei.

8
00:02:10,910 --> 00:02:11,780
"Cheng" for project,

9
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:12,950
"Peng" for ambitious,

10
00:02:12,950 --> 00:02:13,950
and "Fei" for fly.

11
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:25,190
I used to work in the army

12
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:26,310
as a military doctor.

13
00:02:26,310 --> 00:02:28,110
I was initially in the Nanjing Military District

14
00:02:28,110 --> 00:02:28,630
and then transferred to...

15
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:30,260
I dated someone.

16
00:02:30,630 --> 00:02:32,030
You know about it, right?

17
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:34,760
I've heard.

18
00:02:35,420 --> 00:02:37,070
You have such great qualities,

19
00:02:37,070 --> 00:02:38,670
there's no need to act silly.

20
00:02:42,710 --> 00:02:44,230
I was with someone too.

21
00:02:46,110 --> 00:02:47,340
All I did was

22
00:02:48,140 --> 00:02:49,030
held hands

23
00:02:53,579 --> 00:02:54,670
and kissed once.

24
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:13,600
[Staff Cafeteria]

25
00:03:10,540 --> 00:03:14,040
[September 1982]

26
00:03:48,950 --> 00:03:50,030
Yaya.

27
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:52,930
Good boy.

28
00:03:55,470 --> 00:03:57,820
How did the name Hong Kong come by?

29
00:03:58,060 --> 00:03:59,230
It's so nice.

30
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:05,550
There are so many skyscrapers.

31
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,030
They build them so tall,

32
00:04:07,030 --> 00:04:08,380
wouldn't they worry about them collapsing?

33
00:04:08,380 --> 00:04:09,290
What does that have to do with us?

34
00:04:09,290 --> 00:04:10,350
We can't go either.

35
00:04:11,030 --> 00:04:12,070
Why not?

36
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,640
I didn't mean that.

37
00:04:15,950 --> 00:04:17,180
Our kids are still young, aren't they.

38
00:04:17,180 --> 00:04:18,190
When they grow up,

39
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:19,709
they can bring you there.

40
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,320
Can I even count on them?

41
00:04:21,930 --> 00:04:23,930
I'm lucky if they don't hold me back.

42
00:04:25,940 --> 00:04:27,020
Hong Kong.

43
00:04:28,350 --> 00:04:30,280
I have to visit once no matter what.

44
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:36,040
