How is your result?

81
00:06:35,420 --> 00:06:36,090
Mine...

82
00:06:37,150 --> 00:06:39,520
Mine isn't released yet.

83
00:06:40,180 --> 00:06:41,710
The papers for senior students are harder.

84
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:43,409
The teachers take longer to mark them.

85
00:06:43,409 --> 00:06:43,950
Really?

86
00:06:44,390 --> 00:06:45,050
But why do I heard that

87
