better than during rehearsal.

132
00:08:55,550 --> 00:08:55,950
Yeah.

133
00:08:55,950 --> 00:08:57,510
Just now Li Si made two mistakes.

134
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:59,200
A minor injury won't stop one from being on the frontline.

135
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,270
I performed with an injury.

136
00:09:00,270 --> 00:09:02,070
Nonetheless, I didn't drag the team down.

137
00:09:02,070 --> 00:09:03,100
Didn't drag the team down?

138
