You've gotten at least two moves wrong.

139
00:09:04,570 --> 00:09:05,850
What two wrong moves?

140
00:09:06,380 --> 00:09:07,170
Listen up.

141
00:09:07,350 --> 00:09:08,720
This is a big event.

142
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:09,760
I heard that the chosen performances

143
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:10,580
get to be performed

144
00:09:10,580 --> 00:09:12,640
at Qingdao Stadium on the 1st of July.

145
00:09:13,230 --> 00:09:13,790
Really?

146
00:09:13,790 --> 00:09:14,430
Of course.

147
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:16,270
How many are they choosing?

148
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:17,810
They're saying

149
00:09:17,810 --> 00:09:19,480
even if only one performance gets chosen,

150
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,570
it has to be us.

151
00:09:21,870 --> 00:09:23,080
Who said that?

152
00:09:23,110 --> 00:09:24,150
Zhu Chao said it.

153
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:27,310
Zhu Chao?

154
00:09:28,710 --> 00:09:30,420
Hey, don’t look down on Zhu Chao.

155
00:09:30,420 --> 00:09:32,080
When Zhu Chao bought lottery tickets for his dad,

156
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,590
he won 50 dollars three consecutive times.

157
00:09:33,590 --> 00:09:34,720
Isn't that amazing?

158
00:09:35,050 --> 00:09:35,630
Really?

159
00:09:35,650 --> 00:09:36,560
It is!

160
00:09:38,410 --> 00:09:39,090
Come on.

161
00:09:39,110 --> 00:09:39,870
Students performing,

162
00:09:39,870 --> 00:09:41,200
please gather outside.

163
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:42,300
The results are out already?

164
00:09:42,300 --> 00:09:42,680
Hurry up.

165
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:44,010
Everyone, gather here.

166
00:09:45,170 --> 00:09:47,480
[Selection Audition for Oilfield's Grand Performance Program]

167
00:09:45,390 --> 00:09:46,210
Students,

168
00:09:46,870 --> 00:09:47,790
this time round,

169
00:09:47,790 --> 00:09:48,990
the team that wins the eligibility to perform,

170
00:09:48,990 --> 00:09:50,750
which our school fought hard to get,

171
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:52,780
will be representing Linqi Oilfield

172
00:09:52,780 --> 00:09:53,830
in Qingdao.

173
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,370
What does this mean?

174
00:09:57,670 --> 00:09:58,710
It means

175
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:01,320
it's not only about our school anymore.

176
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,850
It's about the honour of the entire oilfield.

177
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:04,950
Students,

178
00:10:05,430 --> 00:10:07,090
how great of an honour that is?

179
00:10:14,070 --> 00:10:14,820
So,

180
00:10:15,010 --> 00:10:16,850
after three days of selections,

181
00:10:17,430 --> 00:10:18,870
we have shortlisted three teams

182
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:19,700
as our candidates.

183
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:20,460
Of course,

184
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:21,920
don't be discouraged

185
00:10:22,110 --> 00:10:23,430
if you're not selected.

186
00:10:23,430 --> 00:10:23,950
We can still

187
00:10:23,950 --> 00:10:25,270
still participate in the performance

188
00:10:25,270 --> 00:10:26,730
held here at our oilfield.

189
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,810
I'll announce the list now.

190
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:32,370
The first one is

191
00:10:33,150 --> 00:10:34,940
Little Choir performing

192
00:10:35,110 --> 00:10:36,460
"The Same Old Song".

193
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:39,820
Congratulations, everyone.

194
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:41,320
An amazing job!

195
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,520
Come on.

196
00:10:43,830 --> 00:10:44,830
The second one is

197
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:47,670
The folk dance piece "Young Lady".

198
00:10:49,710 --> 00:10:50,400
It's okay.

199
00:10:50,550 --> 00:10:52,080
There's one more spot left.

200
00:10:53,990 --> 00:10:55,440
And lastly,

201
00:10:55,860 --> 00:10:56,720
the third one is

202
00:10:57,230 --> 00:10:58,190
the musical

203
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,170
"I am the next

204
00:11:03,210 --> 00:11:04,520
proud roughneck".

205
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:18,070
Director.

206
00:11:18,070 --> 00:11:19,270
Practice hard, okay?

207
00:11:19,560 --> 00:11:20,360
Director.

208
00:11:20,730 --> 00:11:23,040
Why didn't our show get chosen?

209
00:11:24,350 --> 00:11:25,390
What do you think?

210
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:28,750
Is it because Li Si didn't dance well?

211
00:11:28,750 --> 00:11:30,280
He got injured two days ago.

212
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:31,900
I just got discharged.

213
00:11:32,100 --> 00:11:33,960
I usually dance better than this.

214
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:36,000
The three of you

215
00:11:36,510 --> 00:11:37,950
are given grace to be allowed

216
00:11:37,950 --> 00:11:39,750
in the preliminary round today.

217
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,080
You guys cheated in your final exam.

218
00:11:43,170 --> 00:11:44,410
Day after day,

219
00:11:44,650 --> 00:11:46,030
you're just up to shady business.

220
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:47,740
Now you even dare to sing and dance?

221
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:50,540
Why don't you work on your studies and discipline?

222
00:11:51,180 --> 00:11:52,380
Your qualification for the preliminary round is cancel.

223
00:11:52,380 --> 00:11:53,830
Wait for the punishment to be announced.

224
00:11:53,830 --> 00:11:54,310
I...

225
00:11:55,890 --> 00:11:56,640
Congratulations.

226
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:58,370
Congratulations to our choir.

227
00:11:58,540 --> 00:12:00,130
You must continue to practice hard

228
00:12:00,130 --> 00:12:01,310
and bring glory to the school.

229
00:12:01,310 --> 00:12:02,150
Do you hear me?

230
00:12:02,170 --> 00:12:03,380
Yes.

231
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:19,310
I'm in huge trouble because of you two.

232
00:12:19,310 --> 00:12:19,950
I've never ever scored zero

233
00:12:19,950 --> 00:12:21,430
in my whole life.

234
00:12:21,450 --> 00:12:22,410
I did,

235
00:12:22,550 --> 00:12:24,190
and it was in third grade.

236
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:26,290
I even ran away from home that time.

237
00:12:26,470 --> 00:12:29,080
How can I bring this home to sign?

238
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:30,550
How about we sign for each other?

239
00:12:30,550 --> 00:12:32,430
We'll be screwed if we bring this home.

240
00:12:32,430 --> 00:12:33,760
What do you think, Miao?

241
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:38,130
Alright, Miao.

242
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:39,490
Stop worrying about it.

243
00:12:39,670 --> 00:12:40,350
The three of us

244
00:12:40,350 --> 00:12:41,500
can't even participate in

245
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:42,370
the performance in the oilfield.

246
00:12:42,370 --> 00:12:43,620
We rehearsed for nothing.

247
00:12:43,620 --> 00:12:44,830
Bought the clothes for nothing too.

248
00:12:44,830 --> 00:12:45,530
Xiaofang

249
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:47,070
has already given us zero marks.

250
00:12:47,070 --> 00:12:47,990
Now she doesn't even let us perform?

251
00:12:47,990 --> 00:12:48,550
I know right?

252
00:12:48,550 --> 00:12:49,870
It's fine if she doesn't let us perform.

253
00:12:49,870 --> 00:12:51,590
But why does she need say it in front of everyone?

254
00:12:51,590 --> 00:12:52,750
She did it on purpose.

255
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:53,860
What's the big deal?

256
00:12:53,860 --> 00:12:55,250
Isn't it just performing a show in Qingdao?

257
00:12:55,250 --> 00:12:56,180
We're not going!

258
00:12:56,990 --> 00:12:57,910
It's Hong Kong's handover.

259
00:12:57,910 --> 00:12:59,280
What's the point of performing in Qingdao

260
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:00,330
as if it's the actual event?

261
00:13:00,330 --> 00:13:02,530
If you're capable, go to Hong Kong then.

262
00:13:08,020 --> 00:13:09,450
You want to go Hong Kong?

263
00:13:16,760 --> 00:13:17,600
Yes.

264
00:13:18,990 --> 00:13:19,830
I haven't been able

265
00:13:19,830 --> 00:13:21,750
to swallow my anger these past couple of days.

266
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:23,030
I kept thinking

267
00:13:23,220 --> 00:13:24,860
what can I do

268
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:26,800
to turn this around?

269
00:13:27,590 --> 00:13:28,630
All Xiaofang wanted

270
00:13:28,630 --> 00:13:30,210
was to embarrass us in public.

271
00:13:30,210 --> 00:13:31,810
So I have to create some drama

272
00:13:31,810 --> 00:13:33,110
to fight against her.

273
00:13:33,140 --> 00:13:33,580
Yes.

274
00:13:33,680 --> 00:13:34,870
Create what drama?

275
00:13:36,890 --> 00:13:37,890
I don't know yet.

276
00:13:38,380 --> 00:13:39,750
But Yaya came up with it.

277
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:42,550
Hitting the vital part directly.

278
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:43,350
Come on, Cheng Yaya.

279
00:13:43,350 --> 00:13:43,860
Tell me.

280
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:45,590
How did you come up with this idea to go to Hong Kong,

281
00:13:45,590 --> 00:13:46,940
which is such a grand decision?

282
00:13:46,940 --> 00:13:47,420
Wait.

283
00:13:47,450 --> 00:13:48,380
What do you mean?

284
00:13:48,940 --> 00:13:49,620
Weren't you the one who said it?

285
00:13:49,620 --> 00:13:50,750
Well said.

286
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:55,340
Waking up the dreamer with one sentence.

287
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:58,120
On July 1st, 1997,

288
00:13:58,150 --> 00:14:00,810
