00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:24,550
"Bye."

861
00:36:24,570 --> 00:36:25,700
Isn't this English?

862
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:27,750
"Hello, everyone."

863
00:36:28,180 --> 00:36:31,060
"My name is Cheng..."

864
00:36:31,090 --> 00:36:33,260
"I..."

865
00:36:33,300 --> 00:36:34,240
Li Si.

866
00:36:34,340 --> 00:36:35,290
Where did you go?

867
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,540
You're not studying at all.

868
00:36:36,540 --> 00:36:37,420
"Hello."

869
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:39,400
As long as you can speak, we are good.

870
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:40,390
There's no need for all four of us

871
00:36:40,390 --> 00:36:40,910
to be fluent

872
00:36:40,910 --> 00:36:42,240
in speaking Cantonese.

873
00:36:42,310 --> 00:36:43,030
Sure.

874
00:36:43,050 --> 00:36:43,920
Then, don't stick with us later,

875
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:44,630
okay?

876
00:36:45,080 --> 00:36:46,280
If I don't stick with you

877
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:47,130
and stay far away from you,

878
00:36:47,130 --> 00:36:48,730
who will buy clothes for you?

879
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:02,920
You stole your dad's cigarettes and alcohol again?

880
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:03,670
I didn't.

881
00:37:03,690 --> 00:37:05,130
Where did you get the money from?

882
00:37:05,130 --> 00:37:06,460
My grandma gave it to me.

883
00:37:06,780 --> 00:37:07,680
You're lying.

884
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:08,830
I know you well.

885
00:37:08,830 --> 00:37:10,090
You bring up your grandma as soon as you lie.

886
00:37:10,090 --> 00:37:11,150
Aren't you afraid I'll tell your dad?

887
00:37:11,150 --> 00:37:13,270
Why can't you distinguish your enemy from your friends?

888
00:37:13,270 --> 00:37:14,900
I really didn't steal my dad's cigarettes and alcohol.

889
00:37:14,900 --> 00:37:16,630
I just cleared

890
00:37:16,650 --> 00:37:18,780
some scraps at home

891
00:37:18,870 --> 00:37:19,800
and reused them.

892
00:37:19,810 --> 00:37:21,000
What scrap?

893
00:37:21,030 --> 00:37:22,560
It's sold for so much money.

894
00:37:29,430 --> 00:37:30,470
I don't need that much money

895
00:37:30,470 --> 00:37:31,510
to buy clothes.

896
00:37:32,120 --> 00:37:33,360
I request that,

897
00:37:33,820 --> 00:37:35,570
because I paid the most,

898
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:37,040
and Yaya did the most work,

899
00:37:37,040 --> 00:37:38,370
when we're on the train,

900
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,880
you two serve me and Yaya.

901
00:37:45,520 --> 00:37:46,230
Sure.

902
00:37:46,330 --> 00:37:47,790
We can take care of you now.

903
00:37:53,150 --> 00:37:53,510
Let's go.

904
00:37:53,510 --> 00:37:55,190
-Great.
-Let's go.

905
00:38:00,990 --> 00:38:02,360
I'm flying.

906
00:38:02,380 --> 00:38:03,310
Let's go.

907
00:38:04,130 --> 00:38:05,370
Be careful.

908
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:08,810
Here.

909
00:38:18,460 --> 00:38:19,060
Hurry up.

910
00:38:19,060 --> 00:38:20,930
What are you doing here hitting things?

911
00:38:20,930 --> 00:38:22,370
I'm fixing your shoes.

912
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:23,500
Aren't they rubbing your feet?

913
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:24,060
That's great.

914
00:38:24,060 --> 00:38:24,880
Can you try them on?

915
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:25,630
Okay.

916
00:38:25,660 --> 00:38:26,290
I've brought out

917
00:38:26,290 --> 00:38:27,340
-your tuxedo.
-Okay.

918
00:38:27,340 --> 00:38:28,240
Try them on first.

919
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:28,720
Okay.

920
00:38:31,230 --> 00:38:31,870
Not bad.

921
00:38:31,900 --> 00:38:32,940
Pretty good.

922
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:33,800
Alright, let's leave now.

923
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:34,400
Hurry up.

924
00:38:34,430 --> 00:38:34,940
We're running late.

925
00:38:34,940 --> 00:38:35,870
Yaya.

926
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:36,840
Miaomiao.

927
00:38:36,870 --> 00:38:38,270
Make your own food, okay?

928
00:38:38,290 --> 00:38:40,290
I'm going to rehearse with your dad.

929
00:38:40,870 --> 00:38:42,710
There are instant noodles in the cabinet.

930
00:38:42,710 --> 00:38:43,730
Have you gotten everything?

931
00:38:43,730 --> 00:38:45,080
Yes.

932
00:38:45,530 --> 00:38:46,530
Let's go.

933
00:39:13,190 --> 00:39:14,520
Cheng Yaya, hurry up.

934
00:39:17,230 --> 00:39:17,660
Let's go.

935
00:39:17,660 --> 00:39:18,360
Where is the note?

936
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:18,960
The note.

937
00:39:19,070 --> 00:39:19,900
Here.

938
00:39:31,950 --> 00:39:34,100
The ones heading to Linchuan Train Station,

939
00:39:34,100 --> 00:39:34,840
if you haven't gotten on the bus,

940
00:39:34,440 --> 00:39:38,910
[Waiting Area]

941
00:39:34,870 --> 00:39:36,370
hurry up and get on.

942
00:39:37,790 --> 00:39:39,830
The ones heading to Linchuan Train Station,

943
00:39:39,830 --> 00:39:40,590
if you haven't gotten on the bus,

944
00:39:40,590 --> 00:39:42,300
hurry up and get on.

945
00:39:42,650 --> 00:39:43,710
You got the ticket?

946
00:39:44,520 --> 00:39:45,450
Is it at the back?

947
00:39:50,380 --> 00:39:50,840
Ticket.

948
00:39:51,470 --> 00:39:52,250
Slow down.

949
00:39:54,160 --> 00:39:55,640
We can't escape

950
00:39:55,670 --> 00:39:57,270
the beating this time round.

951
00:39:57,390 --> 00:39:58,120
Go ahead.

952
00:39:58,220 --> 00:39:59,750
Have I not gotten it enough?

953
00:40:00,490 --> 00:40:02,350
We're not running away from home.

954
00:40:03,060 --> 00:40:04,570
We're simply on a

955
00:40:04,590 --> 00:40:05,850
vacation internship.

956
00:40:06,160 --> 00:40:07,240
We're already seventeen

957
00:40:07,240 --> 00:40:08,660
and we have not left this place once.

958
00:40:08,660 --> 00:40:10,460
Why can't we go outside and see the mountains

959
00:40:10,460 --> 00:40:11,080
and the sea?

960
00:40:11,080 --> 00:40:12,160
The world is so big.

961
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:13,530
Let's go and have a look.

