00:41:02,110 --> 00:41:02,910
What's wrong?

971
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:05,840
I want to use the toilet.

972
00:41:08,700 --> 00:41:09,430
Hang in there.

973
00:41:09,430 --> 00:41:10,730
We're almost at the train station.

974
00:41:10,730 --> 00:41:12,210
I can't hold it in anymore.

975
00:41:18,240 --> 00:41:19,880
Sir.

976
00:41:20,110 --> 00:41:22,360
Please stop over at the tree.

977
00:42:25,060 --> 00:42:27,120
Our first time running away from home

978
00:42:27,150 --> 00:42:28,280
is to go to Hong Kong.

979
00:42:28,520 --> 00:42:30,050
We were ignorant and crazy.

980
00:42:30,230 --> 00:42:32,280
We did all the preparation we needed

981
00:42:32,380 --> 00:42:33,770
to go to the big city.

982
00:42:34,110 --> 00:42:36,350
Cheng Yaya made a full plan.

983
00:42:36,510 --> 00:42:38,510
