00:42:50,830 --> 00:42:52,310
But, back in the days,

993
00:42:52,480 --> 00:42:53,410
broadening our horizon

994
00:42:53,410 --> 00:42:55,710
is a luxury

995
00:42:55,920 --> 00:42:57,250
to a kid from the rurals.

996
00:42:57,800 --> 00:43:00,130
I've been to many places after growing up.

997
00:43:00,230 --> 00:43:01,390
But no one have since accompanied me

998
00:43:01,390 --> 00:43:02,590
carrying my backpack

999
00:43:02,720 --> 00:43:04,950
and sing the song "Alone to Have Fun".
